lenders.loan_because: I am aware that all that has been given to me, does not belong to me.
lenders.occupational_info: I try to make a task easier and faster, without having to work harder.

lenders.name: Judy
lenders.loan_because: I love the idea of having a positive impact on someone who doesn't even know you, a world away. While Globalization has many detractors, one of its strengths is bringing people together in philanthropy. I am enthralled to be part of the process and I have to thank Nikolas Kristof from the NewYork Times for making me aware of this opportunity.
lenders.occupational_info: I am a forensic pathologist. I perform autopsies to figure out why people die. I also counsel grieving families and explain to them what happened to their loved ones.

lenders.name: Susan
lenders.loan_because: We have more to share than we sometimes realize

lenders.name: Mike
lenders.loan_because: Someone once told me that if you can't save the whole at once, save it one person at a time, and the people you save can also make a difference. Kiva is that starting point for me.
